1
00:00:00,320 --> 00:00:02,600
This place brings back so many memories.

2
00:00:03,640 --> 00:00:05,280
What are you doing?

3
00:00:06,280 --> 00:00:08,040
Oh, is this about revenge?

4
00:00:08,160 --> 00:00:09,280
Are you going to tell
the alumni here,

5
00:00:09,280 --> 00:00:11,800
that Iijima Sami
is a terrible person?

6
00:00:12,160 --> 00:00:13,600
And the current students and teachers?

7
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:15,200
Tell everyone you see?

8
00:00:16,360 --> 00:00:19,640
That's so pathetic.
That's not what this is about, is it?

9
00:00:19,760 --> 00:00:23,320
I want to hear the truth
from your own mouth.

10
00:00:23,760 --> 00:00:25,440
The truth about what?

11
00:00:25,480 --> 00:00:27,640
That you're the daughter of
the President of Kurogane Holdings,

12
00:00:27,960 --> 00:00:29,520
Kurogane Samon.

13
00:00:29,720 --> 00:00:31,680
That you did it to protect me,

14
00:00:32,120 --> 00:00:34,320
to keep me safe from President Kurogane.

15
00:00:35,040 --> 00:00:36,920
That's why you rejected me in high school.

16
00:00:36,920 --> 00:00:38,240
What are you talking about?

17
00:00:38,240 --> 00:00:39,440
I won't accept that!

18
00:00:39,680 --> 00:00:41,200
Not an excuse like that!

19
00:00:42,040 --> 00:00:43,360
Why would you do that?

20
00:00:43,360 --> 00:00:44,600
By doing that,

21
00:00:44,600 --> 00:00:45,840
you're the only one who gets to feel noble.

22
00:00:45,840 --> 00:00:47,240
I'm not happy about it at all!

23
00:00:47,240 --> 00:00:48,240
This has nothing to do

24
00:00:48,240 --> 00:00:49,440
with being happy.

25
00:00:49,680 --> 00:00:50,680
That man...

26
00:00:50,680 --> 00:00:52,120
There's no telling what he would have
done to you.

27
00:00:52,120 --> 00:00:52,760
A father like that...

28
00:00:52,760 --> 00:00:54,120
I needed you to tell me

29
00:00:54,160 --> 00:00:55,800
the truth.

30
00:00:55,840 --> 00:00:57,200
If I had told you,

31
00:00:57,360 --> 00:00:59,480
you would have tried to protect me,
wouldn't you?

32
00:00:59,640 --> 00:01:01,480
I couldn't let that happen.

33
00:01:01,480 --> 00:01:02,800
What he might have done to you...

34
00:01:02,800 --> 00:01:04,320
What if you had gotten hurt?

35
00:01:04,720 --> 00:01:07,000
Why are you always
the one worried about me?

36
00:01:07,240 --> 00:01:08,440
You got hurt too!

37
00:01:08,440 --> 00:01:10,160
You were hurting
too, weren't you?

38
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:13,640
No, I wasn't. I know
I'm rich.

39
00:01:13,760 --> 00:01:14,880
I have a handsome husband.

40
00:01:14,880 --> 00:01:16,040
And I live a carefree life.

41
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:16,800
I'm perfectly happy!

42
00:01:16,800 --> 00:01:17,800
Liar!

43
00:01:18,080 --> 00:01:20,040
Then why do you have
that look on your face?

44
00:01:20,240 --> 00:01:21,800
I don't.
I look perfectly normal.

45
00:01:21,880 --> 00:01:23,800
Then why did you
kiss me like that?

46
00:01:24,880 --> 00:01:26,280
Why did you kiss me?

47
00:01:26,600 --> 00:01:27,920
It's because you have feelings for me!

48
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:28,880
I do not have feelings for you!

49
00:01:28,880 --> 00:01:30,280
Stop flattering yourself!

50
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:31,280
I'm not flattering myself.

51
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:32,760
What is wrong with you?
Why won't you just admit it?

52
00:01:32,760 --> 00:01:34,920
This isn't about admitting
anything.

53
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:36,440
You think I'm still hung up

54
00:01:36,440 --> 00:01:37,240
on what happened in high school,

55
00:01:37,240 --> 00:01:38,280
do you?

56
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:40,680
Then what
is this?

57
00:01:41,080 --> 00:01:43,480
This... uh...
it's just...

58
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:44,360
I just like it, that's all.

59
00:01:44,360 --> 00:01:46,640
You're still holding on!
You miss our high school days.

60
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:47,840
And you miss me!

61
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:49,360
Look who's talking!

62
00:01:49,360 --> 00:01:51,400
Your finger!
Look at your finger!

63
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:52,080
It's nothing!

64
00:01:52,240 --> 00:01:53,280
Why are you still wearing it?

65
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:54,080
Because I like it!

66
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:55,760
Didn't you say
you wanted revenge?

67
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:57,760
I did say that!
I want revenge!

68
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:59,120
Don't you hate me?

69
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:00,520
I hate you, I hate you, I hate you!

70
00:02:00,520 --> 00:02:01,920
You said you were going to
push me into the abyss,

71
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:02,520
didn't you?

72
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:04,000
This is all your fault, Sami.

73
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:04,560
Now,

74
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:05,560
I can't trust anyone anymore!

75
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:07,040
Just get out of my sight.

76
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:08,160
Disappear!

77
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:09,160
It's safer that way!
